$ Powershell command noun: winLanguageBarOption

The `winLanguageBarOption` manages a → Windows/user-account[user's] *language bar mode* and *languabe bar type*.

Commands related to the → Windows/PowerShell[PowerShell] command noun `winLanguageBarOption`:
  • `get-winLanguageBarOption`
  • `set-winLanguageBarOption`

code {
PS C:\> get-winLanguageBarOption

IsLegacyLanguageBar IsLegacySwitchingMode
------------------- ---------------------
              False                 False
code }

